term: mix of raw material for the purpose of further processing
original_definition: 'mix of raw material for the purpose of further processing' means the physical mixing of raw material for the sole purpose of producing biofuels, bioliquids or biomass fuels;
generated_definition: 'mix of raw material for the purpose of further processing' means a combination of raw materials used as input for manufacturing, processing, or production.
